'''菲利普·亞當斯'''（Phillip Adams，{{bd|1988年|7月20日|2021年|4月8日|catIdx=Adams}}）是美国职业[[美式足球|美式足球]]运动员，曾在[[國家美式橄欖球聯盟|國家美式橄欖球聯盟]]（NFL）担任{{link-en|角卫|Cornerback}}。他曾在{{link-en|大學橄欖球聯賽|College football}}上代表南{{link-en|卡罗来纳州牛头犬队|South Carolina State Bulldogs football}}參加比賽，并在{{link-en|2010年NFL选秀|2010 NFL Draft}}中的第七轮被[[舊金山49人|舊金山49人]]选中。他还曾效力于[[新英格兰爱国者|新英格兰爱国者]]、[[奧克蘭突擊者|奧克蘭突擊者]]、[[西雅图海鹰|西雅图海鹰]]、[[纽约喷气机|纽约喷气机]]和[[亞特蘭大獵鷹|亞特蘭大獵鷹]]。

2021年4月7日，菲利普·亞當斯在[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]][[石山_(南卡罗来纳州)|石山]]槍殺5人、槍伤6人<ref name="ap_04082021">{{Cite news|title=Authorities: NFL player Phillip Adams killed 5, then himself|url=https://apnews.com/article/phillip-adams-kills-5-then-himself-south-carolina-aaf71f2618f139ab3781592634c8e37c|accessdate=8 April 2021|work=AP NEWS|date=8 April 2021}}</ref><ref name="cnbc">{{Cite web|title=NFL pro Phillip Adams kills five, then himself|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/04/08/nfl-pro-phillip-adams-kills-five-then-himself.html|accessdate=2021-04-08|date=2021-04-08|work=CNBC}}</ref><ref name="independent">{{Cite web|title=Ex-NFL player reported as gunman who killed renowned doctor and grandchildren|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/phillip-adams-south-carolina-shooting-nfl-b1828474.html|accessdate=2021-04-08|date=2021-04-08|work=The Independent}}</ref><ref name="foxnews">{{Cite web|title=Ex-NFL player Phillip Adams' father on South Carolina shooting: 'I think the football messed him up'|url=https://www.foxnews.com/sports/nfl-phillip-adams-father-south-carolina-shooting|accessdate=2021-04-08|author=Gaydos|date=2021-04-08|first=Ryan|work=Fox News}}</ref><ref name="wcnc">{{Cite web|title=Father of York County shooting suspect says son killed 5 others, then himself|url=https://www.wcnc.com/article/news/crime/york-county-doctor-mass-shooting-phillip-adams-suspect-father-identifies-son/275-2fa8b949-1a7f-4a86-a90b-2223b595a756|accessdate=2021-04-08|work=wcnc.com}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.wcnc.com/article/news/crime/york-county-doctor-mass-shooting-phillip-adams-suspect-father-identifies-son/275-2fa8b949-1a7f-4a86-a90b-2223b595a756 "Father of York County shooting suspect says son killed 5 others, then himself"]. ''wcnc.com''<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">April 8,</span> 2021</span>.</cite></ref>。4月8日，亚当斯在与警方对峙時开枪自杀。亞當斯的父親表示，亞當斯的美式足球生涯可能在枪击案中起到了作用，亞當斯的父親還表示这项运动把他毀了<ref name="wcnc"/>。

